snippet.title: Dead Cells: Netflix Edition | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
You're a pile of undead sludge. Find a body, uncover secrets and defeat bosses to escape a deserted castle. If you die, restart and reignite the fight.

Play Dead Cells: Netflix Edition on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: http://www.netflix.com/game/81705117

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 247 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Dead Cells: Netflix Edition | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix
